// Decorative ribbed bracket (derived from ribbed_bracket_nm.bp)
//
// vs. benchmark model:
//   - Stronger crest/trough on shared seam [12,13,14,15].
//   - Rib **bottom** row [113,114,115] duplicates wall top [101,102,103] (same XYZ) so the
//     wall–rib boundary is one shared Bézier (VerifyCurveGeometry). Left column stays [12,13,14,15]
//     (NM seam with base); do not use 113–115 on the left column or pt01/pt10 collapse at 12.
//   - Far rib edge [118,121] and right column [122,123,124] follow the same wave in Y,
//     with Z at wall levels (1.333, 2.667, 4) on the outer column.
